        {
          "lang": "zh-TW",
          "lang_word": "alarm",
          "definition": "n. 警報、警鈴、驚恐  v. 使驚恐、使擔憂"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "The fire alarm went off during the meeting, forcing everyone to evacuate the building.",
