            "zh-TW": "會議期間火災警報響起，迫使所有人撤離大樓。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "The sudden drop in sales alarmed the board of directors.",
          "highlight": [
            "alarmed"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "銷售額突然下滑令董事會感到驚恐。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "The rate at which the company is losing customers is alarming the shareholders.",
          "highlight": [
            "alarming"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "公司流失客戶的速度正令股東感到憂心。"
          }
        }
